[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

With 22 points you should open 2\C. Partner responds 2\D.  

You have 22 points and 5-card Major suit. Your rebid is therefore 2\S. Partner raises to 4\S. His jump to game shows a weaker hand than a 3\S bid would so you pass.}

